VisualWidth
===========

This is a unicode character's visual width calculator for javascript.

This module supports node.js, too.

SYNOPSIS
--------

    var vw = require('./visualwidth');
    console.log(vw.width('あいうabc')); # => 9
    console.log(vw.truncate('ほう。hasegawaさん', 7, '...'));  => "ほう..."

